a unique internal mechanism.

335
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:27,400
The mechanism and its components

336
00:30:27,560 --> 00:30:28,800
have a certain weight.

337
00:30:29,290 --> 00:30:31,210
So it causes the house suspended
in mid-air

338
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:32,730
to tilt slightly.

339
00:30:33,080 --> 00:30:34,320
So I used a steel ball

340
00:30:34,770 --> 00:30:36,640
