of the house.

341
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,210
Then I searched around

342
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,450
and found the mechanism

343
00:30:39,450 --> 00:30:40,800
by accident.

344
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:44,160
Get that? That's my way of doing things.

345
00:30:44,600 --> 00:30:45,730
Naive has never

346
00:30:45,840 --> 00:30:48,600
let anyone down before.

347
00:30:50,600 --> 00:30:51,530
He was lucky.

348
00:30:52,730 --> 00:30:54,930
Exactly, it's infuriating enough.

349
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:04,880
Let's go.

350
00:31:07,800 --> 00:31:08,930
Here we come.

351
